title: Berner and San Quinn - Cookies & Cream (ALBUM)
description:
San Francisco legends Berner and San Quinn were bound to hook up and collaborate eventually and now the time has come. On Cookies & Cream the pair creates an instant classic. Guests include Baldhead Rick, Big Tone, June Summers, Ralph Davis, Lucky Luciano, Young Boss, Equipto, Lee Majors, Amp, Matt Blaque and more. *****2013*****

04. Berner & San Quinn ft. Ralphy Davis - Freeze (Prod. By Biggz)

05. Berner & San Quinn ft. Ampichino, Freeze & Smiggz - Play To Win (Prod. By DJ Fresh)

09. Berner & San Quinn ft. Matt Blaque & Mike Marshall - Summertime (Prod. By Stingy)
